ly larger than those observed in\nquantum mechanical studies. Possible impacts of the observed over-polarization\nof the ions on simulated anion surface segregation are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2009 16:49:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2009 16:57:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
