ever, this is the first such formula\nfor the Askey-Wilson polynomials, which are at the top of the hierarchy of\nclassical orthogonal polynomials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2009 21:04:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2011 15:11:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2013 19:12:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-27"}
